    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Applewood Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">A beautiful and tranquil residential community located within the south-east quadrant of Calgary. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Applewood Park is renowned for the GlobalFest fireworks that are held at the Elliston Park on the south west</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Given the fact that it is only recently developed, the community consists of top notch public amenities and modern conveniences that make life easy and stress-free for its residents.</p>

